- Assert row_count(), column_count() funcionan
- Assert cell access funciona

TEST: test_element_variants_exhaustive
- Crear uno de cada: Title, Paragraph, Table, Header, Footer, ListItem, Image, CodeBlock, KeyValue
- Assert cada uno tiene discriminante correcto via matches!()

TEST: test_element_metadata_defaults
- Create Element con metadata default
- Assert page=0, confidence=1.0, bbox es zero-rect
- Assert font_info es None

TEST: test_element_metadata_with_font
- Create Element::Title con font metadata (bold, size 24)
- Assert font info accesible

TEST: test_element_ordering_by_position
- Crear 3 elements con diferentes page/y positions
- Sort por orden natural (page ASC, y DESC para reading order)
- Assert orden correcto

TEST: test_element_debug_display
- Create Element::Title
- Assert Debug output contiene "Title"

TEST: test_element_clone
- Create Element, clone, comparar igualdad

TEST: test_element_bbox_accessors
- Create Element con bbox (10, 20, 100, 50)
- Assert x(), y(), width(), height(), right(), top()
```

**Implementation file**: `oxidize-pdf-core/src/pipeline/element.rs`

Nuevo modulo `pipeline` en `oxidize-pdf-core/src/pipeline/mod.rs`:
```rust
pub mod element;
pub use element::{Element, ElementBBox, ElementMetadata};
```

Element enum:
```rust
pub enum Element {
    Title(ElementData),
    Paragraph(ElementData),
    Table(TableElementData),
    Header(ElementData),
    Footer(ElementData),
    ListItem(ElementData),
    Image(ImageElementData),
    CodeBlock(ElementData),
    KeyValue(KeyValueElementData),
}
```

ElementData:
```rust
pub struct ElementData {
    pub text: String,
    pub metadata: ElementMetadata,
}

pub struct ElementMetadata {
    pub page: u32,
    pub bbox: ElementBBox,
    pub confidence: f64,
    pub font_name: Option<String>,
    pub font_size: Option<f64>,
    pub is_bold: bool,
    pub is_italic: bool,
}
```

