- CREATE: `oxidize-pdf-core/src/pipeline/reading_order.rs`
- MODIFY: `oxidize-pdf-core/src/pipeline/mod.rs`
- MODIFY: `oxidize-pdf-core/src/pipeline/partition.rs` (usa ReadingOrderStrategy)
- CREATE: `oxidize-pdf-core/tests/reading_order_test.rs`

